  "title": "Giant Chocolate Cornflake Cookies",
  "subtitle": "Crisp at the edges, soft in the middle.",
  "excerpt": "Giant Chocolate Cornflake Cookies. A baking recipe from Rebecca's collection, straightforward, reliable, worth weighing rather than scooping.",
