      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Giant Chocolate Cornflake Cookies. An American family-table recipe, generous, comforting, built for a crowd. Serves 20.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Cookies bake fast and reward a chilled dough. Pull them out when the edges set and the middles still look slightly underdone.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
